      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still has that 'new car' feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one. I'd love for you to come by and take a look; you won't be disappointed!",
