    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and pampered since day one. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in a set of premium tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the leather upholstery is supple and matte, showing no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that fresh, new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at a certified dealership. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, showing no signs of leaks or wear. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is, for all intents and purposes, brand new.",
